## Build

Use any LaTeX distribution with `pdflatex` and BibTeX:

```bash
pdflatex main.tex
bibtex main
pdflatex main.tex
pdflatex main.tex
```

Or use the Makefile:

```bash
make
```

Or use `latexmk`:

```bash
latexmk -pdf main.tex
```

