This package includes four paper-ready TikZ figures:

- `figures/i2os_context.tikz` - SIV25 as a discourse-structure layer of I2OS
- `figures/social_role.tikz` - structural role against biased, narrative, and AI-generated discourse
- `figures/compression_matrix.tikz` - matrix projection from 25 meters to UI4
- `figures/pipeline.tikz` - full 25 -> 7 -> 5 -> 4 pipeline
- `figures/example_ui4.tikz` - example input and UI4 structural rendering

